name: Dumb Rocket Game: the dwayne heist
name_original: Dumb Rocket Game: the dwayne heist
description:
This is a very terrible game, but it taught me a lot while making it.

I only put effort into level 6, so you can press "L" to skip a level if you want.

BTW the web version will only work properly if you go 100% fullscreen, and i've only tested it on 1080p so idk how it would fare on other resolutions ¯\_(ツ)_/¯

(you should really just download the windows version tbh)
